name: Outlaws of Thunder Junction Commander Deck Desert Bloom

sealed.name: Outlaws of Thunder Junction Collector Booster Sample Pack

product.name: Outlaws of Thunder Junction Commander Deck - Desert Bloom
product.cleanName: Outlaws of Thunder Junction Commander Deck Desert Bloom

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
In Outlaws of Thunder Junction, your players will join Oko's crew of deadly desperados as they plot a heist in the frontier world of Thunder Junction. They'll face harsh deserts, hostile critters, and even rival outlaws—but with grit and gumption, they'll ride off into the sunset.
In Commander, four players come together to show their strength and strategy, with one player coming out on top. Each 100-card ready-to-play Outlaws of Thunder Junction Commander Deck makes it easy for Commander fans in your store to grab a deck and play right away.?
Contents:
• 1 ready-to-play deck of 100 Magic cards (2 Traditional Foil Legendary cards, 98 nonfoil cards)
• 2-card Collector Booster Sample Pack
• 10 new-to-Magic cards
• 10 double-sided tokens
• 1 deck box (can hold 100 sleeved cards)
• 1 Life Wheel
• 1 strategy insert
• 1 reference card
